Welcome:
- XML has become a widely used standard for storing and exchanging information on the internet.
- Knowing how to work with XML has become a core skill that every developer needs to have.
- In this course we will learn:
  * What XML is and does
  * Some of its advantages and drawbacks
  * We will create and style XML content using a variety of approaches
    - CSS
    - Using the browser's DOM
  * Investigate complimentary XML technologies
    - XPath, XSLT
  * How these can be used to manipulate XML content
  * How to use document type definitions and XML schema to help ensure that
    XML data is error free.
